    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">431 Stevens street</name>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">Camden New Jersey<ptr target="prc.00060_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1880-11-17" rend="right"><choice><abbr>Nov:</abbr><expan>November</expan></choice> 17</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>My dear friend</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I do myself the real pleasure of presenting you with a set of my books&#8212;which are sent by same mail with this&#8212;I have inscribed Mrs G's name with yours on the fly leaf, &#38; please show her this as a testimony of my remembrance &#38; affection to you both<ptr target="prc.00060_n2"/>&#8212;</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            
            <postscript>
                <p>I am well for me&#8212;have been down two weeks in the Jersey woods&#8212;return'd last evening&#8212;</p>
            </postscript>         
        </body>
    </text>
